            <title>[LU-18923] move osd-ldiskfs cache parameters from debugfs to sysfs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18923</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are several &quot;simple&quot; osd-ldiskfs parameters (just a single numeric value) that are located in debugfs that should be moved over to sysfs:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;readcache_max_filesize&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;readcache_max_io_mb&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;writethrough_max_io_mb&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
